385
00:15:17,480 --> 00:15:19,440
Paul cared about these people.

386
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:20,920
He said, I didn't write that letter

387
00:15:20,920 --> 00:15:22,320
because of the one that was wrong

388
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:24,079
or the one that was wronged.

389
00:15:24,079 --> 00:15:26,480
He says that the motivation, if you will,

390
00:15:26,480 --> 00:15:28,079
and obviously we know that all scripture

391
00:15:28,079 --> 00:15:29,799
is given by inspiration of God,

392
00:15:29,799 --> 00:15:32,239
but he says that our care for you in the sight of God

393
00:15:32,239 --> 00:15:34,160
might appear unto you.

394
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:37,600
He says in verse 13, therefore,

395
00:15:37,600 --> 00:15:41,239
we are comforted in your comfort,

396
00:15:41,239 --> 00:15:45,640
yea, and exceedingly the more joyed we

