00:15:45,640 --> 00:15:48,839
for the joy of Titus because his spirit

398
00:15:48,839 --> 00:15:51,760
was refreshed by you all.

399
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:55,239
So he's talking about how they as a church,

400
00:15:55,239 --> 00:15:58,359
how they refreshed and encouraged Titus

401
00:15:58,359 --> 00:16:02,660
and Paul's saying we were comforted in your comfort

402
00:16:02,660 --> 00:16:06,760
because you comforted Titus and then Titus came to us

403
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:08,399
and Titus comforted us.

404
00:16:08,399 --> 00:16:10,760
I mean, God is at work in this thing.

405
00:16:12,239 --> 00:16:15,000
He says that his spirit was refreshed by you all

406
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:18,799
for if I, verse 14, have boasted anything to him of you,

