00:16:31,279 --> 00:16:33,920
He's trying to take from them the idea

414
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:35,359
of some of those false teachers

415
00:16:35,359 --> 00:16:39,600
that would try to get them to turn against Paul,

416
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,880
that Paul say, no, I've not done

