442
00:17:39,920 --> 00:17:40,839
So what's Paul saying?

443
00:17:40,839 --> 00:17:44,279
I rejoice therefore that I have confidence in you

444
00:17:44,279 --> 00:17:45,720
in all things.

445
00:17:45,720 --> 00:17:47,559
That they would be doers of the word,

