00:18:43,960 --> 00:18:46,559
sometimes the complexity of that relationship

468
00:18:46,559 --> 00:18:49,239
reaches higher levels.

469
00:18:49,239 --> 00:18:53,719
The relationship between children and their parents.

470
00:18:53,719 --> 00:18:57,520
The relationship between adult children and their parents.

471
00:18:58,520 --> 00:19:00,239
It's complicated, it's complex.

472
00:19:00,239 --> 00:19:01,080
Why?

