00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:03,440
Because you're not what you were

474
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:05,880
when you were that two-year-old running around, right?

475
00:19:05,880 --> 00:19:07,479
You understand the complexity.

476
00:19:07,479 --> 00:19:11,479
Listen, relationships change over time.

477
00:19:11,479 --> 00:19:15,880
The dynamics, the complexity of relationships.

478
00:19:15,880 --> 00:19:18,440
How about the relationships between church members?

479
00:19:19,359 --> 00:19:20,200
Amen?

480
00:19:20,200 --> 00:19:22,359
Listen, we come from different backgrounds.

481
00:19:22,359 --> 00:19:24,520
We come from different upbringings.

482
00:19:24,520 --> 00:19:27,719
We have different perspectives that we bring to the table.

483
00:19:27,719 --> 00:19:29,559
Different likes and dislikes.

484
00:19:29,559 --> 00:19:31,340
We could talk about music.

485
00:19:31,340 --> 00:19:32,919
We could talk about preference

486
00:19:32,919 --> 00:19:34,159
and we could talk about those things.

487
00:19:34,159 --> 00:19:39,159
And we have to understand the complexity of relationships.

488
00:19:39,159 --> 00:19:41,919
We think about music and to just touch on that

