00:19:47,960 --> 00:19:50,400
there's definitely within that spectrum,

492
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:53,760
there's right music and there's wrong music.

493
00:19:53,760 --> 00:19:56,359
And within that spectrum of right music,

494
00:19:56,359 --> 00:19:58,159
there's gonna be a preference.

495
00:19:59,000 --> 00:20:00,359
And your preference might.

496
00:20:00,359 --> 00:20:04,419
be on this side of it, and someone else's preference might be over here, but overall

