00:20:04,419 --> 00:20:08,459
it's still within the category of good, godly music.

498
00:20:08,459 --> 00:20:12,059
It may not be your preference.

499
00:20:12,059 --> 00:20:16,659
The complexity of relationships, do you understand what I'm saying?

500
00:20:16,659 --> 00:20:22,939
And we begin to consider the color of a carpet, the color of a pew, the curtains, the lighting,

501
00:20:22,939 --> 00:20:24,059
the this, the that.

