00:20:24,059 --> 00:20:27,779
Listen, these things can become extremely complicated.

503
00:20:27,779 --> 00:20:32,259
I remember when we first moved into our townhouse, and many of you went to the townhouse.

504
00:20:32,259 --> 00:20:36,699
We have open house for our church family every year at Christmas time, and many of you were

505
00:20:36,699 --> 00:20:37,699
there.

506
00:20:37,699 --> 00:20:40,539
If you didn't come for that, oftentimes we invite folks to our home for dinner, so on

