513
00:21:08,819 --> 00:21:12,899
Can you move that one over there, and move this one over here?

514
00:21:12,899 --> 00:21:18,099
And so here I am with Joseph, you know, nine years old, trying to help me move this furniture,

515
00:21:18,099 --> 00:21:22,339
and we're moving the furniture, and we get it in the position that Holly wants, and she

